The meaning of Anusuya is the one who is void of envy;

39
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:42,400
she does not envy anyone,

40
00:02:43,300 --> 00:02:45,300
who is the universal love

41
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:48,280
In such a person there is no place for insignificant,

42
