This tejbal fell on them

52
00:03:22,100 --> 00:03:23,800
and they became small children.

53
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:27,340
Their complete unified form is Shri Datta Maharaj.

54
00:03:27,340 --> 00:03:28,880
He is a strange majesty ,

55
00:03:29,100 --> 00:03:31,440
whatsoever description is made of him but will fall short.

56
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:34,680
