57
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:38,200
This is Shri Datta Maharaj who is full of triguna (three attributes).

58
00:03:38,620 --> 00:03:41,380
He came in the world in form of Adiguru many times

59
00:03:41,460 --> 00:03:43,600
to teach how to cross the Bhavsagara (void).

60
00:03:43,900 --> 00:03:47,040
