73
00:04:52,080 --> 00:04:57,180
Mohammad means Praise, the one who is praised, the one who deserves to be praised

74
00:04:57,420 --> 00:05:01,400
and is the one who is redeemer of the world

75
00:05:01,620 --> 00:05:06,840
They were all Mohammads, they were all Dattatreyas,

76
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:10,580
who came on earth regularly.

77
00:05:12,020 --> 00:05:14,280
After that Nanaka, Guru Nanaka.

78
00:05:15,020 --> 00:05:16,880
If you ever read his teachings,

79
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:19,280
if you read his talks

80
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:23,620
then you will be surprised that he has always talked in a Sahaja.

81
00:05:23,860 --> 00:05:26,040
