82
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:33,360
He has said, ‘kahe re ban khojan jayi, sada niwasi sada alepa tohe sang samai,

83
00:05:33,540 --> 00:05:41,940
pushpa madhya jo was basat hai mukur mahi jas chhayee, taise hi hari base nirantar ghat hi khojo bhai’

84
00:05:41,940 --> 00:05:43,480
- why to go to forest to find Him,

85
00:05:43,540 --> 00:05:46,040
He is always there with you just like there is a fragrance in a flower

86
00:05:46,100 --> 00:05:48,100
and just as the reflection is there in a mirror,

87
00:05:48,100 --> 00:05:49,840
in the same way God is residing in you eternally seek Him within.

88
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,720
He is just inside, achieve him just inside.

89
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:53,340
We are just singing poem, singing songs, we are just cramming his prescription.

90
00:05:53,340 --> 00:05:55,940
The talk of seeking this absolute principle, residing just inside the heart, has been made since ancient times

91
00:05:55,940 --> 00:06:00,980
by these Adi Gurus, who are incarnated on this earth again and again.

92
00:06:01,980 --> 00:06:05,460
After the birth of the daughter of Mohammad Sahab,

93
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:10,220
as I talked yesterday also, there was beginning of the caste “Shia” in Islam.

